current-chamber.#text: IN THE SENATE OF THE UNITED STATES

official-title.#text:
Providing for the reappointment of John W. McCarter as a citizen regent of the Board of Regents of
			 the Smithsonian Institution.

cosponsor.#tail: ) introduced the following joint resolution; which was read twice and referred to the

{http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml}enti.#tail:
, in the class other than
			 Members of Congress, occurring by reason of the expiration of the term of
			 John W. McCarter of Illinois on March 14, 2014, is filled by the
			 reappointment of the incumbent.  The reappointment is for a term of 6
			 years, beginning on March 15, 2014, or the date of enactment of this joint
			 resolution, whichever occurs later.
